title: Downtown Naperville 2BR 1.5BA Bsmt Garage

Updated 2 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom duplex, two stories, in quiet neighborhood near restaurant district, with furnished washer and dryer in 1st floor half bath.

1 garage space plus 1 outside parking space.
